# Revision 1.5  2002/01/31 00:33:13  pwagner
# Prefixes preset paths just like forwaard model
#
# Revision 1.4  2001/11/15 00:07:57  pwagner
# Now works with new libmlspack.a and .mod files in blas
#
# Revision 1.3  2001/10/22 18:30:56  pwagner
# Added l_special like l2
#
# Revision 1.2  2001/08/15 21:03:28  pwagner
# Default rules for .f and .c; EXTRA_PATHS added to INC_PATHS
#
# Revision 1.1  2001/05/31 22:06:28  pwagner
# Repaired omission of .f from SUFFIXES
#
# Revision 1.5  2001/03/12 23:57:45  pwagner
# New FAFTER, LAFTER flags to postprocess compile & link steps
#
# Revision 1.4  2001/02/26 21:14:38  pwagner
# Commented out FOPTS assignment; now part of .configure setting
#
